{"tid":444178,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】車cam影低愛驅遭刮花一刻 車主冀目擊者助緝兇","createTime":"2017-10-22T09:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T05:25:59.000Z","uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c70195f29ebbdbc269edb327e020926f301b406b","tid":444178,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:41:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nqCnIKcH4MA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnqCnIKcH4MA&d=QyXU194jRvXZQ7BW7U48Z4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=b165d436\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nqCnIKcH4MA</a><br />\n<br />\n屯門有車主愛驅遭人蓄意刮花！有網民在facebook上載相片及片段，可見一名男子途經其私家車車頭時，用物件在車頭蓋刮了一道長長刮痕，該網民已報警，並表示希望附近的商舖及事發時在附近的車主可協助緝兇。<br />\n<br />\n該網民昨在facebook貼文稱，事發在昨晚10時23分，屯門虹橋青翠徑發生。車cam影片所見，一名體型略胖，事發時身穿黑色Polo恤的男子行近事主車頭時，右手疑拿著物件，並放在車頭蓋上，劃出一道刮痕後離開，期間曾回頭一看。貼文者亦上載一張照片，顯示車頭蓋上有明顯的白色長刮痕 <br />\n<br />\n巴打們小心睇車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21f6b97c8f62727f3c980f7dbb7e6f7cf658ac9","tid":444178,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:45:20.000Z","msg":"拉左未"},{"pid":"87bff1ad37aa62fe05087ed50b977c52c1d01c8a","tid":444178,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"更多內容請前往：<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/544950-香港-【有片】車cam影低愛驅遭刮花一刻+車主冀目擊者助緝兇\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F544950-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E8%BB%8Acam%E5%BD%B1%E4%BD%8E%E6%84%9B%E9%A9%85%E9%81%AD%E5%88%AE%E8%8A%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%88%BB%2B%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%BB%E5%86%80%E7%9B%AE%E6%93%8A%E8%80%85%E5%8A%A9%E7%B7%9D%E5%85%87&d=QyXU194jRvXZQ7BW7U48Z4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3fcf773c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F544950-%E9%A6%99%E6%B